---
title: Caesar-Style Chicken & Bacon Burger with Caramelised Onion & Mayo
description: Bring on the weekend with a show-stopping, mouth-watering Caesar-style sauce and caramelised bacon-topped chicken burger.
And don’t overlook the chunky potato wedges. This dinner is bound to become a part of your warmer weather repertoire!
